{"tid":934158,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"公屋戶做愛叫聲大惹人不滿　鄰居：晚上喺走廊乜都聽到","createTime":"2018-12-09T05:14:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-09T07:19:16.000Z","uid":159163,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"61fa781ded5234b62daad0484c5f7a988a030b06","tid":934158,"uid":159163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T05:14:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20181208/large/1544261471_4174.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20181208%2Flarge%2F1544261471_4174.jpg&h=d1815317&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能真的是土地問題，連在私人空間做的私人事，也會影響到別人。<br />\n<br />\n「麻煩叫床唔好咁大聲！！」屯門蝴蝶邨有居民懷疑難忍鄰居叫床聲過太，在門前貼上字條投訴。該邨亦有居民表示，一直都受嘈音問題滋擾，「晚上喺走廊乜都聽到」。<br />\n<br />\n網上流傳一張相片，見到有人在門前鐵閘貼上致蝴蝶邨某單位的字條，要求對方注意叫床聲。本刊記者曾到過現場，貼上字條的單位無人應門，而鄰近的街坊禤小姐就表示，這裡的單位隔音欠佳，即使關着門亦能聽見隔壁的聲音，如果大聲一點，更能清楚聽到別人的對話，「睡覺的時候會很清楚聽到鄰居拉鐵閘的聲音。」<br />\n<br />\n街坊陳先生說，未曾聽見鄰居的叫床聲，見到網上流傳的相片，覺得驚奇，不過他坦言有時候小朋友經過走廊，便會有點嘈吵。<br />\n<br />\n至於網上就引來熱烈討論，有網民表示近來愈來愈多同類投訴，亦有網民笑說可能鄰居只是看成人影片音量過大。<br />\n<br />\n港男張先生表示，如果他遇到同類情況，為免影響鄰里關係，不會去投訴，「又不用貼字條這麼誇張，個個行過都見到。」他又說做愛正常都會發出聲音，聽到亦不會感到尷尬。<br />\n<br />\nBonnie亦表示聽到亦無所謂，不過如果有朋友或男性在身邊的時候，便會有點尷尬。她說：「我覺得他自己都會知道那麼大聲，相信他不會日日不斷這樣做，一個月一兩次的話我能接受。」<br />\n<br />\n另一港男阿賢就同情被騷擾鄰居，指他可能經常被滋擾，太大心理陰影才出些下策，不過他認為貼字條未必有效，應該向管理員投訴。"},{"pid":"83b16a8591beb45eae4981222dd2cade373e09c3","tid":934158,"uid":159163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T05:14:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/magazine/article/20181209/2_642377_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20181209%2F2_642377_0&d=nx7H5sf570SoxVOA%2BJ9gjTM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=5e440b9c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20181209%2F2_642377_0&h=1f9a0528\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/magazine/article/20181209/2_642377_0</a>"},{"pid":"49059fd040f556a452ce63764bbd742d8b5e9e9a","tid":934158,"uid":52323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T05:15:33.000Z","msg":"@撚狗俠"},{"pid":"7e8d2f2ef9f4e375aad376f06292a5040268819c","tid":934158,"uid":10692,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T05:16:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eb610b000db76f0e86090e90d6d958bb9c87cefc","tid":934158,"uid":14797,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T05:16:39.000Z","msg":"吾你老母<br />\n甘你老母"},{"pid":"00d1a23048e256f275d9d09d58a1795db49dc7aa","tid":934158,"uid":159163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T05:35:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d5a8be8d04f344b26de8b8553e9b6ee0ac56e7d","tid":934158,"uid":3028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T05:37:20.000Z","msg":"唔抵得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4b0b394a527cb3ce76feee92ebe2eeeada16fa5","tid":934158,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T05:45:44.000Z","msg":"想聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d34810d728ec618ad05102ff607cdb7baf80462f","tid":934158,"uid":8858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T05:47:52.000Z","msg":"有live咁正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過廢中廢老就不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7314ee927a6a16fb85806151086aef91ff96224a","tid":934158,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb610b000db76f0e86090e90d6d958bb9c87cefc","tid":934158,"uid":14797,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T05:16:39.000Z","msg":"吾你老母<br />\n甘你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201